section.section:
To assist the Corporation in complying with subsection (c) of this section, the Governor shall include each year in the State budget bill an appropriation to the Corporation for rural business development and assistance as follows:
for fiscal year 2011, $2,750,000;
for fiscal year 2012, $2,750,000;
for fiscal year 2013, $2,875,000;
for fiscal year 2014, $2,875,000; and
for each of the fiscal years 2015 through 2020, $4,000,000.
